this is a tool for handling your files using command line tool

1. copy this file into your:  protected/commands directory

2. edit your file protected/yiic.php, pay attention to the config file,
the used one must have the fileman component registered on it.

3. check README.md for details in usage:

	cd yourapp
	cd protected
	./yiic fileman --cmd=list --id=123456	< list files
	./yiic fileman --cmd=add --id=123456 --files=/var/tmp/file1,/home/myfile1

